overview: A young dancer and Unity member, Parker Herring, along with Bob McKenna, challenges the ever present questions of existence, love, death, sexuality, nudity and nature. Through his practice of living in the unknowable he discovers what is conscious, what is intuitive and how nothing is ever assured.
tagline: The boundless nature of reality, the essence of every energetic thing, the lights, the people, the consciousness that brings all of it together...
title: Sea of Abundance
